So about 2012, the
National Partnership

00:26:47.670 --> 00:26:52.440
for Maternal Safety and
ACOG, and 30 organizations

00:26:52.440 --> 00:26:55.230
came together to try
and address this issue.

00:26:55.230 --> 00:26:58.890
And they have cranked out
about 10 bundles of care.

00:26:58.890 --> 00:27:00.600
Recommendations for
how do you treat

00:27:00.600 --> 00:27:05.190
hemorrhage, how do you treat
postpartum hypertension.

00:27:05.190 --> 00:27:10.680
And about a year ago-- or
maybe this past summer--

00:27:10.680 --> 00:27:12.600
there was an article
in the USA Today

00:27:12.600 --> 00:27:17.370
that said hospitals know what
to do, why aren't they doing it?

00:27:17.370 --> 00:27:22.680
And that really shook both
